  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00267', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '已知某國國內生產毛額（GDP）與支出面資料如下：（單位：千億元） 2016年 2017年 民間消費 90 80 資本形成 30 40 政府消費 30 20 商品及服務輸出 100 120 商品及服務輸入 50 60 GDP平減指數（2011年=100） 100 102 2017年此國家的名目GDP成長率為：', '["1%", "0.5%", "0%", "–0.5%"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4c296907e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4f3eb1fbbf91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "141", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00268', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '原物料的價格增加，在短期將造成：', '["一般物價水準及實質GDP均增加", "一般物價水準增加及實質GDP減少", "一般物價水準下降及實質GDP增加", "一般物價水準及實質GDP均下降"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4c296907e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4f3eb1fbbf91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "141", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00269', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為名目GDP與實質GDP的差別？', '["折舊", "物價上漲率", "失業率", "生產力變動"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4c296907e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4f3eb1fbbf91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "141", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00270', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '原油價格、出口、投資、生產技術、自然災害等，這5項的衝擊變動都可能造成景氣循環。此5項中 屬於供給面衝擊的有幾項？', '["1項", "2項", "3項", "4項"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4c296907e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4f3eb1fbbf91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "141", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00271', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據凱因斯學派，世界各國之所以會發生景氣循環，主要是因為下列何者？', '["政府政策失當", "理性預期無法形成", "技術變動", "市場機能無法發揮"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4c296907e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4f3eb1fbbf91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "141", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00272', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲、乙兩國，儲蓄率、人口成長率、資本折舊率都相同。甲國人均所得是乙國的2倍，但甲國人均所 得的成長率卻不到乙國人均所得成長率的一半。這一個現象符合下列何種理論？', '["馬爾薩斯理論", "新興凱因斯理論", "新古典經濟成長理論", "理性預期理論"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4c296907e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4f3eb1fbbf91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "141", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00273', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於一個採取浮動匯率制度國家，若它的出口大於進口，在無統計誤差下，則該國的經常帳餘額為 _____，而資本與金融帳餘額為_____。', '["入超：淨資本流入", "出超：淨資本流出", "出超：淨資本流入", "出超：資訊不足無法確定是淨資本流入或淨資本流出"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4c296907e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4f3eb1fbbf91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "141", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-7fec267e-moex-00274', 'customs-7fec267e', 'customs-7fec267e-moex-111-6948958a', 'sub-customs-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '當購買力平價成立時，若本國物價下跌，其他條件不變下，本國通貨價值_____，本國通貨兌外國通 貨匯率應要_____。', '["低估；下跌", "高估；下跌", "高估；上升", "低估；上升"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9e4c296907e5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4f3eb1fbbf91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111050", "c": "141", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
